        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Critical Infrastructure Act</b></p> <p>This bill imposes an enhanced general penalty on any person who is sentenced to imprisonment for violating certain communications laws and who willfully or maliciously destroys any communications facility during and in relation to such violation. </p>]]>
        </text>
